00:04:40.070 --> 00:04:45.030
The best part about the rental boom, is that
due to artificially low interest rates, we

00:04:45.030 --> 00:04:49.660
are seeing an anomaly. ***Rising rents while
real wages are down***

00:04:49.660 --> 00:04:55.000
Landlords are becoming more and more recession
resistant by the day. With low vacancy rates,

00:04:55.000 --> 00:05:00.860
high demand, and effective rents increasing,
now may be the best time to become a landlord.

